[User Opens Gmail Email]
           ↓
[Content Script Injected]
           ↓
[Extension Scans Email Body Text]
           ↓
[Parse for Dates, Times, Keywords (like "meeting", "due", "event")]
           ↓
[If Match Found → Show Popup on Email Page]
           ↓
[Popup says: "Add to Calendar?" → [Add] or [Edit]]
           ↓
[If Add → Use Google Calendar API to Create New Event]
           ↓
[Confirmation Message: "Event Added! ✅"]